snippet.title: Evercade 'Atari Collection 1' Cartridge Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit: http://evercade.co.uk/atari-collection-1/

The 'Atari Collection 1' cartridge brings 20 classic Atari 2600 and Atari 7800 games to the Evercade! The cartridge will be supplied in a stunning collectable retro style physical case with full colour manual.

Featuring:
Centipede (2600)
Missile Command (2600)
Alien Brigade (7800)
Adventure (2600)
Ninja Golf (7800)
Food Fight (7800)
Motor Psycho (7800)
Crystal Castles (2600)
Desert Falcon (2600)
Tempest (2600)
Asteroids (2600)
Canyon Bomber (2600)
Gravitar (2600)
Double Dunk (2600)
Steeplechase (2600)
Video Pinball (2600)
Night Driver (2600)
Aquaventure (2600)
Swordquest Earthworld (2600)
Yars Return (2600)
